Package: spectropath
Type: Package
Title: Path-Signature Diagnostics for Spectral-Line Morphology
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Rafael",
    family = "S. de Souza",
    email = "rd23aag@herts.ac.uk",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Rafael S. de Souza [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Rafael S. de Souza <rd23aag@herts.ac.uk>
Description: Companion tools for representing astronomical spectral features
    as ordered paths and extracting low-order path-signature diagnostics of
    line-profile morphology. The package exposes the paper-facing quantities
    used to describe signed area, weighted asymmetry, higher-order modulation,
    and emission--absorption ordering, plus classical line-profile descriptors
    for benchmarking and machine-learning workflows.
